76561198072380091,Not Recommended,305840,18729401,"Posted: 28 October, 2015",all,whatdoesthisbuttondo?,"Unfortunately, I have to change my review to not recommended. I'll refrain fromspeculation here on what / who / how, but there has been complete radio silencefrom the devs for quite a while, and my gut feeling says this project might be deadat this point.-----original review below-----Just launched on EA and still in early alpha stage, I wouldn't recommend it for a general audience yet as there is only a limited set of the features to come implemented. It currently features a small portion of the ships/weapons/modules that will be available, two skirmish battle missions you can play on four maps, and ship customization designer.Having said that, it has huge potential and is on track to become the definite must-have spacefleet battle simulator game of 2016. Sitting kinda in-between the strategic elements of Homeworld and the tactical focus of Nexus, it is a nice breath of fresh air for the genre."
